[Student "S"]
{With your hand you'd like to sign off in 3\D. But you cannot actually bid 3\D because that would show a forcing-to-game hand. So you bid a lebensohl 2NT.

Partner makes the relay bid of 3\C.  

NOW you can bid 3\D, which partner passes.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "W"]
[Vulnerable "EW"]
